headline: Genuine Parts Company to Present at the UBS Global Consumer and Retail Conference
summary: Genuine Parts Company (NYSE: GPC), a leading global service provider of automotive and industrial replacement parts and value-added solutions, announced today that Bert Nappier, EVP & CFO, will present at the 15th Annual UBS Global Consumer and Retail Conference at 10:00 a.m. ET on Wednesday, March 11, 2026.
